nodes.text: Ipisestec was a location in the galaxy that featured the Mororororosc Valley. Athlete Manac-Nebut hailed from Ipisestec.

Ipisestec was mentioned in Monsters and Aliens from George Lucas, a book published in 1993. Lucasfilm employee Leland Chee, who maintains the Holocron continuity database, has indicated that information contained in the book is non-canonical.
